      @alm
      Feature: Application and Device Type Management in Bundles

        As a user of the portal UI
        I want to be able to upload applications and device type bundles
        So that I can operate the Portal devices

        Background:
          Given I am logged in as an administrator from the platform org
          And I am on the DASHBOARD page
          And I select the bundles option from the top navbar
          And I should see the BUNDLES_LIST page
          And I select the NEW button
          And I should see the BUNDLES_UPLOAD page

        @M2M-ALM-114
        Scenario: Uploading Device Type in Bundles
          When I use the form to upload the GAS_METER_DEVICE_BUNDLE_1 file
          Then I should see a list that matches the following:
            | Bundle ID Bundle Type Bundle Name Bundle Description Version                                    |
            | GasMeterBundle1 Device Gas Meter Bundle 1 Metron Metrix 250 CHF Gas Meter Bundle Metron 250-1 1 |
